verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Complete in Thee
No work of mine
May take dear Lord
The place of Thine
Thy blood hath pardon
Brought for me
And I am now
Complete in Thee

verse.name: c1
verse.lines:
Yes justified -
O blessed tho't
And sanctified
Salvation wrought
Thy blood hath pardon
Bought for me
And glorified
I too shall be

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Compete in Thee
No more shall sin
Thy grace hath conquered
Reign within
Thy voice shall bid
The tempter flee
And I shall stand
Complete in Thee

verse.name: v3
verse.lines:
Complete in Thee
Each want supplied
And no good thing
To me denied
Since Thou my portion
Lord will be
I ask no more
Complete in Thee

verse.name: v4
verse.lines:
Dear Savior when
Before Thy bar
All tribes and tongues
Assembled are
Among Thy chosen
Will I be
At Thy right hand
Complete in Thee
